<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Defs>
    <!-- colossus -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="ProtossMechanoid">
    <defName>PMP_ColossusPrototype</defName>
    <label>Purifier colossus</label>
    <description>Unlike the simplified models that followed, this towering war machine is a prototype Purifier Colossus, one of the first to enter mass production. Khalai scientists claim that it is the design closest to the Protoss Titans of the Golden Age. Taller, larger, and far more complex, it houses an AI Personality Core with computational power rivaling a planetary mainframe, is clad in impenetrable Adanium armor, and is serviced by a swarm of nano-reconstructive drones for battlefield repairs. Its twin prototype Thermal Lances project a devastating stream of hyper-thermal plasma, carving through neutronium plating like a hot knife through butter and incinerating the very ground beneath its targets. \n\n The Purifier Colossus is deployed only to Apocalypse-class war zones. In conflicts of such intensity, even genetically engineered super-soldiers are little more than antsâ€”disposable assets used to plug the gaps in a crumbling frontline.</description>
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>12.6</MoveSpeed>
      <BandwidthCost>6</BandwidthCost>
      <ArmorRating_Blunt>1.5</ArmorRating_Blunt>
      <ArmorRating_Sharp>1.5</ArmorRating_Sharp>
    </statBases>
    <race>
      <body>PMP_ColossusBody</body>
      <mechWeightClass>UltraHeavy</mechWeightClass>
      <baseBodySize>8</baseBodySize>
      <baseHealthScale>6.25</baseHealthScale>
      <lifeStageAges>
        <li>
          <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
          <minAge>0</minAge>
          <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Wounded</soundWounded>
          <soundAngry>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Call</soundAngry>
          <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Death</soundDeath>
          <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Call</soundCall>
        </li>
      </lifeStageAges>
    </race>
    <butcherProducts>
      <PM_Adanium>150</PM_Adanium>
    </butcherProducts>
    <comps>
      <li Class="ProtossMech.CompProperties_ProtossMechShield">
        <energyMax>100</energyMax>
        <energyGainPerTick>0.25</energyGainPerTick>
        <ticksToBeginRecharge>600</ticksToBeginRecharge>
        <minDrawSize>0</minDrawSize>
        <maxDrawSize>5</maxDrawSize>
        <!-- <HardenedShields>true</HardenedShields> -->
      </li>
      <li Class="ProtossMech.CompProperties_PurifierReconstruct">
        <cooldownTicks>3600</cooldownTicks>
        <reconstructHediff>Hediff_Reconstruct</reconstructHediff>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>

  <PawnKindDef ParentName="ProtossMechanoidKind">
    <defName>PMP_ColossusPrototype</defName>
    <label>Purifier colossus</label>
    <race>PMP_ColossusPrototype</race>
    <combatPower>42</combatPower>
    <allowInMechClusters>false</allowInMechClusters>
    <lifeStages>
      <li>
        <bodyGraphicData>
          <texPath>Things/Pawn/Mechanoid/colossus</texPath>
          <shaderType>Cutout</shaderType>
          <drawSize>5.0</drawSize>
        </bodyGraphicData>
      </li>
    </lifeStages>
    <weaponMoney>9999~9999</weaponMoney>
    <weaponTags>
      <li>ThermalLances</li>
    </weaponTags>
    <techHediffsChance>1</techHediffsChance>
    <techHediffsMoney>9999~9999</techHediffsMoney>
    <skipResistant>true</skipResistant>
  </PawnKindDef>

  <!-- PurifierImmortal -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="ProtossMechanoid">
    <defName>PMP_PurifierImmortal</defName>
    <label>PurifierImmortal</label>
    <description>Purifier Immortals are armed with twin Phase Disruptors, weapons that inflict damage by destabilizing the very space their target occupies. This disruptive effect intensifies against denser materials, meaning the stronger the enemy's armor, the more catastrophic the resulting impact. These noble warriors charge fearlessly into the heart of the fiercest firefights, advancing steadily through hails of gunfire behind thick Adanium plating and Hardened Shields. Even if their battle chassis is structurally compromised, an integrated swarm of reconstructive nanites can rapidly reassemble the unit on the battlefield, allowing it to fight anew.</description>
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>5</MoveSpeed>
      <BandwidthCost>4</BandwidthCost>
      <ArmorRating_Blunt>1.5</ArmorRating_Blunt>
      <ArmorRating_Sharp>1.5</ArmorRating_Sharp>
    </statBases>
    <race>
      <body>PMP_ImmortalBody</body>
      <mechWeightClass>Heavy</mechWeightClass>
      <baseBodySize>4</baseBodySize>
      <baseHealthScale>5.0</baseHealthScale>
      <lifeStageAges>
        <li>
          <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
          <minAge>0</minAge>
          <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Wounded</soundWounded>
          <soundAngry>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Call</soundAngry>
          <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Death</soundDeath>
          <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_Apocriton_Call</soundCall>
        </li>
      </lifeStageAges>
    </race>
    <butcherProducts>
      <PM_Adanium>125</PM_Adanium>
    </butcherProducts>
    <comps>
      <li Class="ProtossMech.CompProperties_ProtossMechShield">
        <energyMax>100</energyMax>
        <energyGainPerTick>0.25</energyGainPerTick>
        <ticksToBeginRecharge>600</ticksToBeginRecharge>
        <minDrawSize>0</minDrawSize>
        <maxDrawSize>3</maxDrawSize>
        <HardenedShields>true</HardenedShields>
      </li>
      <li Class="ProtossMech.CompProperties_PurifierReconstruct">
        <cooldownTicks>3600</cooldownTicks>
        <reconstructHediff>Hediff_Reconstruct</reconstructHediff>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>

